{
  "description": "Bottom-up mergesort engine — one merged element copied per tick from an aux snapshot over a bar array on algorithm-canvas; composed by a learning orbital via `uses`.",
  "ledger": {
    "entries": {
      "ent_01KXG0513F6HE8VZ7P6B018RVZ": {
